description: The Garcia's Paella Truck comes from the heart of Spanish and Cuban cooking. The Garcia's are making amazing lunch and dinner dishes like a traditional Spanish Paella Mixta, a mix of Fish, Chicken, Mussels, fresh Shrimp, Clams, Calamaris, rice and vegetables that makes for a beautiful meal. If you're feeling the need for Cuban cuisine the Garcia's food truck offers a Cuban menu that has the best flavors the Caribbean has to offer. The making of such dishes are no easy task, specially when it comes to taking it on the road. It takes lots of passion, the best ingredients and skilled hands to design a elegant Spanish and Cuban menu. Next time you are in Hialeah, Florida make your way over to a great meal at Garcia's Paella!
name: Garcia's Paella Food Truck
